                            @{b}@{u}What do I get?@{ub}@{uu}


After paying the fee you will receive a keyfile and the latest version of
Marathon. Furthermore the registrated version includes (when available)
the Marathon Landscape-editor and examples for creating your own Landscape
and all used objects (like cars, planes, etc.). Newer versions of Marathon
will add @{" more stuff " Link Future} to the game (computerplayers, more weapons, etc., etc..)


@EndNode
 

@Node "Update"
@Next "Pay"
@Prev "Get"
@Toc "Main"

                        @{b}@{u}How do I get updates?@{ub}@{uu}


Updates and new Landscapes will be published through AmiNet. If you don't
have access to AmiNet, you can send @{" me " Link Author} a letter, including an empty
disk and 2$ (inside Europe) or 3$ (outside Europe). All I ask from you 
in return is to be a registered Marathon-user.

ATTETION: Orders without disk and/or p&p-money can't be fulfilled!

@EndNode
 

