@Node "Hardware"
@Next "Software"
@Prev "Software"
@Toc "Main"

                          @{b}@{u}Required hardware@{ub}@{uu}


You need the following hardware to run the game:

 - An Amiga (surprise, surprise)
 - 68020+
 - 1MB chip
 - Amiga OS Version 37 or higher (Not tested)
 - Harddisk recommended



Marathon is tested on the following configurations:

    A2000/030/40/40/7   - Kickstart 3.0
    A4000/030/25/25/10  - Kickstart 3.0


Please let @{" me " Link Author} know if you've got another systemconfiguration and although
meeting the above requirements still have problems using this game.


@EndNode

